	(231, 1, 1, 3, 4, 'HSIB', 'Horison Suite & Residences Iswara Bekasi', 'Horison Suite & Residences Iswara Bekasi', '3', 'Jl. Cut Mutia No.2, Sepanjang Jaya, Kec. Rawalumbu, Kota Bks, Jawa Barat', '17114', '081905950000', '081905950000', '081905950000', '081905950000', 'fo.iswarabekasi@horisonhotelsgroup.com', 'HDR_0003.jpg', '<p>Hotel Suites Residences Iswara Bekasi offers luxury and comfort for guests seeking an exceptional stay. Strategically located in the heart of Bekasi, this property features modern suites equipped with comprehensive amenities, including a swimming pool, fitness center, lounge and a restaurant with warmth hospitality and professional service. Horison Suites Residences Iswara Bekasi is the perfect choice for both business and urban travellers.</p>', 'Horison Suite & Residences Iswara Bekasi, Bekasi', 1, 106.99687865887037, -6.259790874946142, '2024-06-11 08:21:13', '2024-07-03 03:49:37');
